{"tid":1363282,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"羅塞洛在波多黎各持續多日示威後屈服　宣布辭任總督","createTime":"2019-07-25T06:29:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T06:50:45.000Z","uid":33618,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"eb4febe9a16c21fbb6b9085912b51ce59aeb0cdf","tid":1363282,"uid":33618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T06:29:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1470382_1_L_20190725141340.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1470382_1_L_20190725141340.jpg&h=c50d234c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美屬波多黎各總督羅塞洛，在當地持續一個多星期的示威後，宣布辭職，下星期五正式離任，確保權力順利交接。羅塞洛說假如繼續出任總督，過去取得的成功將難以維持下去。在首府聖胡安，大批民眾知道羅塞洛辭職後，擁到街上慶祝。<br />\n<br />\n羅塞洛早前被揭發在通訊軟件上，與政界盟友利用歧視女性及同性戀者的字眼，批評其他官員、政客及記者。大批民眾連日上街要求他立即辭職，當地星期一的集會有數十萬人參與，防暴警察一度使用胡椒噴霧和催淚彈，驅趕示威者。<br />\n<br />\n羅塞洛曾透過社交網站向公眾道歉，但堅持留任，最終在強大民意下落台。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1470382-20190725.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1470382-20190725.htm&d=9aIS%2Fhk2hxf5w8hb7WAMUcTiFwqRwBg1VWT7Je45URE%3D&h=82cc719c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1470382-20190725.htm&h=a690978f\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1470382-20190725.htm</a><br />\n#香港人加油"},{"pid":"5168fa1a483f4078c7e5ef7c8ced218edc0f1bb2","tid":1363282,"uid":207574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T06:50:45.000Z","msg":"幾日就收皮 跟林奠學下啦"}]}